ActsAsAudited
=============

Simulates a deleted model using the deleted_at attribute.
Model must have a deleted_at attribute or similar.

Configuration options
=====================
{:deleted_at => "deleted_at"}

Example
=======

class Node < ActiveRecord::Base                                                 
  acts_as_deleted
end



